Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.62,0:01:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.29,0:01:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从中国运过来的金丝猴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.69,0:01:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,额头、胸口和手脚内侧都有着金色的毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是非常珍贵的猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.53,0:01:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这只金丝猴预定在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄武动物公园开放参观到明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.47,0:01:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说明天就决定是金丝猴的摄影大会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？明天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.44,0:01:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暑假突然开始召集人家我还以为是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.51,0:01:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体强制参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.25,0:02:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驳回！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.65,0:02:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那明天10点在玄武动物公园集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不准溜掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.72,0:02:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听别人说话啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.79,0:02:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十八话  同衾（同床共眠）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？不能一起去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.06,0:02:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 因为有洗衣服等很多事情非做不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.51,0:02:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理员要工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.51,0:02:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙要确认屋顶的修理工程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不用现在就做啊 维持现状不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.65,0:02:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说屋顶会漏水的是蒂娜你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也不用今天做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.02,0:02:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,师傅说今天好像会下雨 所以决定提前开始动工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.39,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看大家都很忙的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.53,0:02:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能看到金色的猴子只到今天为止对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来之后再告诉我长什么样子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东跟小妙都不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了啦 把不愉快的事情忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.45,0:03:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来 小铃铃跟阿佐还真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.53,0:03:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 有邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？这次又发生什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,铃木要去兴奋不已的电车祭典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.90,0:03:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿佐要去Cosplay偶像心跳梦幻秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.84,0:03:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？那群浑蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然溜掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.68,0:03:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我昨晚还高兴期待的睡不着觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了啦 不要生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天一天就陪你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 去看金丝猴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.14,0:04:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一时还不知道该怎么办 心情能恢复真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 企鹅企鹅耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小企鹅也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜你真的很喜欢动物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.39,0:04:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？为什么那么没精神？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钿女 你听我说 大家都不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我是想看金丝猴没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.86,0:04:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过比起那个我更希望大家一起来玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也是没有办法的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有句话叫做七转八倒（灾难接踵而志之意）喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.01,0:04:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要说应该是七转八起（人生有起有落之意）吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 鹤边前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是博学呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.91,0:04:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类总是为了无聊的事情又哭又笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.78,0:04:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 东西好吃就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.42,0:04:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能像这样跟动物对话真的很棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真像蒂娜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.20,0:05:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实物果然有够可爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.37,0:05:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能看到真是太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.67,0:05:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 阿薰 帮我跟金丝猴拍一张吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要拍喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 要拍照吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个再靠近一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.13,0:05:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位大姐会不会认为我们是一对恋人啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.53,0:05:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害羞了 害羞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪个？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是什么的招牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去玩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎来到动物幻想爱与冒险城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个将要分开行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这个危险的热带雨林前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后以热带雨林的终点为目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.67,0:06:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦的秘宝正在着你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个就是热带雨林的终点？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你通过这个雨林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是妖精加布林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.55,0:07:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.19,0:07:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇敢的小姐 你将在这里接受命运的抉择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请从着三扇门中选择一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.50,0:07:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里面的服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会展现出你对你的伙伴的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.57,0:07:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伙伴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你的伙伴是朋友的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就选择黑色门的布偶装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.41,0:07:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是朋友以上 恋人未满的话就选择蓝色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后白色门就是结婚礼服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你们相爱的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果之后到这里的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你选择同样的门的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会给你梦的秘宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧 请选择！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是选蓝色的制服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 是白色的门对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.10,0:07:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办 顺其自然就被带进来穿上这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.55,0:08:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 反正我早就想穿一次看看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不会被阿薰看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.39,0:08:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是好不容易穿了 还是想给他看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是万一阿薰来到这里该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈 不会有这种事的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为是我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.91,0:08:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果对象是我 他是不会选这个房间才对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.79,0:08:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果阿薰打开那扇门进来的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.83,0:08:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰不可能会来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 如果来的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.98,0:09:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿…薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.58,0:09:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌啦 阿薰 没想到你真的会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的没想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此 原来是这回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.23,0:09:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什么时候这样看待我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才我还一直在担心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 真是的 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很痛耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.24,0:09:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 还以为总算从凶暴的鸵鸟手中逃出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鸵鸟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个非常可怕的庞然大物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我千钧一发好不容易才逃来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃来这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么你没有从三扇门里选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三扇？有这种东西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为太慌张根本没注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来我实在是有够惨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种东西有什么好玩的啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（梦的秘宝 动物饼干）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.25,0:10:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐 好像下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要赶快把晒的衣服收进来才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快一点 妙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.77,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也来帮忙 拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.17,0:10:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（对关东地区全区发布豪雨特报）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儿童走失中心的通知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中泽章子的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中泽章子的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请尽快到管理事务所来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸很快就会来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.02,0:10:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雨下的很大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜 我们也差不多该回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.37,0:11:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 在你爸爸来之前大姐姐会一直陪你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.64,0:11:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.71,0:11:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.95,0:11:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于外围环流影响 现在关东一带正下着大雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.69,0:11:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这阵雨将会伴随雷电 且雨势强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏天的暴风雨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.43,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个企鹅啊 那个啊 就滑倒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.54,0:11:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊 企鹅真的很可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见 大姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.78,0:11:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受您照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.19,0:12:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜我们也趁早回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.72,0:12:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.43,0:12:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在由于前方土石崩塌全线不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么时候会恢复通车？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该要到明天的早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.93,0:12:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早上？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到处都关门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也搭不上计程车 真伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果哪里有卡拉OK的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去对面看看 你在这里等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是蒂娜吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.69,0:12:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.93,0:12:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还好吗？有没有淋湿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点淋湿 但是不要紧啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.53,0:12:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过电车停驶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？电车停驶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.94,0:12:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以现在正在找能躲雨的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.14,0:13:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我拜托雅去接你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.85,0:13:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顶多在卡拉OK唱个一晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…一晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.05,0:13:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 虽然说是一晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实也没什么 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.09,0:13:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.43,0:13:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐藤跟铃木也在对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.87,0:13:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 那么小心不要感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.07,0:13:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也帮我向薰问好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有电话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.95,0:13:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是房东打过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵？她很担心吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.99,0:13:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是没事啦 倒是你有找到什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.10,0:14:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（备有卡拉OK）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.17,0:14:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到卡拉OK了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.58,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 真是天助我也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.22,0:14:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里不是卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.26,0:14:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算有卡拉OK也未免…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.49,0:14:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊 无论怎样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是躲雨对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.57,0:14:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊 只是普通的躲雨而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.80,0:15:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什什什什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.10,0:15:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛巾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.01,0:15:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看…看电视吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.78,0:15:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔 这不错喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.09,0:15:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.39,0:15:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我去冲个澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连内裤都湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰也湿的差不多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要不要一起进去啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害羞了啊？真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太嫩了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.52,0:16:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虚幻的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.09,0:16:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,献丑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不错喔 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那下一个换我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候我真的吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？什么时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.77,0:16:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜穿结婚礼服的样子 真的非常漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在说这个干嘛啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为真的是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.99,0:16:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我穿结婚礼服的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.86,0:16:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰你还是第一个看到的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜的新郎会是什么样的人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.87,0:16:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有想过吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 有喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.77,0:16:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的新郎啊 是一个容易感到寂寞的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.78,0:16:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然平常老是摆出一付冷淡的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.18,0:17:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是是个非常温柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使我做了傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也会摆出“真拿你没办法”的表情对我笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.59,0:17:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能和那样的人在一起的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.66,0:17:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还蛮具体的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么住的地方一定是小木屋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.83,0:17:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有湖在旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 然后跟很多小孩子跟动物一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.77,0:17:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是很容易想像到的景象呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.47,0:17:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰真是的 果然很了解我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜为什么那么喜欢动物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为动物不会说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.58,0:17:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果人类不去了解动物的心情的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.79,0:17:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类即使会说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.92,0:17:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不见得会说出真正的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.96,0:17:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道能不能跟之前旅行时的动物再见面啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我不在阿薰会寂寞吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然不会寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.91,0:18:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一年级的时候 蒂娜邀我进摄影社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后大家一起做些傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.01,0:18:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才认为原来大学也有有趣的事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（我去看一下世界 PS.大概一年左右回来…吧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是蒂娜突然就离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去大学就变的有些无聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我能这样高兴的上着大学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是托蒂娜的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.93,0:18:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 请你不要再像那个时候一样突然消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.61,0:18:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种会让人不好意思的话你还真敢说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是都回来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.08,0:18:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是你害的身体又冷了 我再去冲一次澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.16,0:18:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸跟妈妈不会原谅这样的我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.43,0:19:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我…如果是阿薰的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.78,0:19:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰你要不要也去冲一下澡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我去冲个澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.84,0:19:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的蒂娜 总觉得…非常的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.85,0:19:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该怎么做？该怎么做才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在想什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.39,0:19:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说蒂娜只是朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.89,0:19:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是朋友而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.77,0:20:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…这样做果然还是不太好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只把你当成是好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且…我已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.89,0:20:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的…还真像你啊 蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.45,0:20:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚 我睡着了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.05,0:20:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 对喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.02,0:21:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是个很奇怪的夜晚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.49,0:21:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.53,0:21:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 到车站之前 我可以握着你的手吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.57,0:21:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…也没关系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.14,0:21:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.18,0:21:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧 快点回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房东一定在担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.78,0:21:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 我的手会痛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.89,0:21:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是一点都不痛喔
